    {
      "start": 747.72,
      "end": 751.34,
      "text": "One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten."
    },
    {
      "start": 752.34,
      "end": 753.44,
      "text": "네, 번역이요."
    },
    {
      "start": 753.44,
      "end": 753.76,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 754.0,
      "end": 754.84,
      "text": "통역 부탁드릴게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 754.98,
      "end": 755.62,
      "text": "이거 통역이요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 755.78,
      "end": 756.86,
      "text": "이거 통역해야 되는 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 757.34,
      "end": 760.62,
      "text": "하나, 둘, 셋, 넷, 다섯, 여섯, 일곱, 여덟, 열."
    },
    {
      "start": 760.78,
      "end": 762.94,
      "text": "All right, Mr. Percival, go find him."
    },
    {
      "start": 763.18,
      "end": 764.06,
      "text": "Go on."
    },
    {
      "start": 764.44,
      "end": 765.1,
      "text": "Go on."
    },
    {
      "start": 765.1,
      "end": 766.14,
      "text": "좋아, 좋아, Percival."
    },
    {
      "start": 766.48,
      "end": 767.24,
      "text": "자, go find him."
    },
    {
      "start": 767.32,
      "end": 767.84,
      "text": "Go on."
    },
    {
      "start": 768.2,
      "end": 769.48,
      "text": "자, 마이클을 찾아봐."
    },
    {
      "start": 769.48,
      "end": 771.74,
      "text": "And he gives him a hint."
    },
    {
      "start": 771.86,
      "end": 772.16,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 772.36,
      "end": 772.86,
      "text": "Uh-oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 773.06,
      "end": 775.36,
      "text": "He betrays his son and gives the pelican a hint."
    },
    {
      "start": 775.52,
      "end": 775.74,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 776.06,
      "end": 776.9,
      "text": "Oh, he's hiding over there."
    },
    {
      "start": 777.16,
      "end": 777.68,
      "text": "Go over there."
    },
    {
      "start": 777.84,
      "end": 779.02,
      "text": "아주 곧바로 찾아냈어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 779.82,
      "end": 780.88,
      "text": "You told him, Dad."
    },
    {
      "start": 780.94,
      "end": 781.76,
      "text": "You told him."
    },
    {
      "start": 781.76,
      "end": 783.72,
      "text": "아, 아빠가 알려줬죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 783.86,
      "end": 784.88,
      "text": "알려주셨잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 785.54,
      "end": 787.76,
      "text": "네, 여기까지 해석을 해봤습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 787.98,
      "end": 788.52,
      "text": "Dad cheated."
    },
    {
      "start": 788.94,
      "end": 792.22,
      "text": "정말 사이가 더 좋아지는 것 같아요, 부자지간도."
    },
    {
      "start": 792.5,
      "end": 794.1,
      "text": "Yeah, very nice."
    },
    {
      "start": 794.1,
      "end": 794.54,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 794.86,
      "end": 799.72,
      "text": "이렇게 pelican으로 인해서 가족이 훨씬 더 끈끈해지는 장면이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 800.5,
      "end": 801.96,
      "text": "자, 다시 한번 확인해보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 802.6,
      "end": 803.64,
      "text": "It's Mr. Percival."
    },
    {
      "start": 804.18,
      "end": 804.92,
      "text": "He came back."
    },
    {
      "start": 805.78,
      "end": 806.76,
      "text": "He can stay, can't he?"
    },
    {
      "start": 807.59,
      "end": 809.63,
      "text": "Yeah, I suppose we can cope with feeding one."
    },
    {
      "start": 810.66,
      "end": 814.48,
      "text": "From that day on, Mr. Percival refused to ever leave my side."
    },
    {
      "start": 815.04,
      "end": 815.82,
      "text": "Not for an hour."
    },
    {
      "start": 816.54,
      "end": 817.64,
      "text": "Not for a minute."
    },
    {
      "start": 818.4,
      "end": 818.68,
      "text": "Never."
    },
    {
      "start": 819.59,
      "end": 819.91,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 820.29,
      "end": 821.45,
      "text": "You stay here and I'll hide."
    },
    {
      "start": 821.85,
      "end": 822.41,
      "text": "No peeking."
    },
    {
      "start": 822.97,
      "end": 824.39,
      "text": "Make sure he doesn't cheat."
    },
    {
      "start": 824.39,
      "end": 826.15,
      "text": "And count to 10 for him."
    },
    {
      "start": 826.67,
      "end": 834.41,
      "text": "One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten."
    },
    {
      "start": 834.83,
      "end": 836.57,
      "text": "All right, Mr. Percival, go find him."
    },
    {
      "start": 836.89,
      "end": 837.33,
      "text": "Come on."
    },
    {
      "start": 837.93,
      "end": 839.03,
      "text": "You told him, Dad."
    },
    {
      "start": 839.09,
      "end": 839.93,
      "text": "She told him."
    },
    {
      "start": 840.95,
      "end": 843.37,
      "text": "네, 아주 행복한 장면이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 843.87,
      "end": 846.27,
      "text": "근데 이게 계속 이어지면 얼마나 좋을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 846.79,
      "end": 848.09,
      "text": "Yeah, forever."
    },
    {
      "start": 848.49,
      "end": 848.83,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 848.83,
      "end": 852.63,
      "text": "근데 왠지 그러지 않을 것 같은 예감이 살짝 들긴 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 852.87,
      "end": 854.15,
      "text": "Another twist is coming."
    },
    {
      "start": 854.15,
      "end": 860.19,
      "text": "차상희님께서 Very Cute Teacher, 크쌤이라고 보내주셨네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 860.47,
      "end": 861.57,
      "text": "Oh, very cute."
    },
    {
      "start": 861.69,
      "end": 862.71,
      "text": "I like that."
    },
    {
      "start": 862.83,
      "end": 863.69,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 864.25,
      "end": 867.97,
      "text": "네, 오늘도 이렇게 즐겁게 함께해 주셔서 너무너무 감사드립니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 868.21,
      "end": 869.15,
      "text": "I had fun too."
    },
    {
      "start": 869.19,
      "end": 870.15,
      "text": "Yeah, thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 870.57,
      "end": 871.29,
      "text": "See you next Monday."
    },
    {
      "start": 871.67,
      "end": 872.39,
      "text": "I'll see you then."
    }
  ]
}